            <fr:title text="Dedekind cuts">Dedekind cuts</fr:title>
            <fr:taxon>definition</fr:taxon>
            <fr:meta name="source"><fr:link href="/baby-rudin/" title="Principles of Mathematical Analysis" uri="http://localhost:8000/baby-rudin/" display-uri="baby-rudin" type="local">Principles of Mathematical Analysis</fr:link>, Appendix to Ch. 1</fr:meta>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
            <html:p>A <html:dfn>Dedekind Cut</html:dfn> is a subset <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\alpha \subset \mathbb {Q}]]></fr:tex> such that:
<html:ol><html:li><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\alpha ]]></fr:tex> is not empty and also <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\alpha \neq \mathbb {Q}]]></fr:tex></html:li>
<html:li>If <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[p\in \alpha ]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[q\in \mathbb {Q}]]></fr:tex> with <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[q<p]]></fr:tex>, then <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[q\in \alpha ]]></fr:tex></html:li>
<html:li>If <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[p\in \alpha ]]></fr:tex>, then there exists some <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[r\in \alpha ]]></fr:tex> such that <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[r\in \alpha ]]></fr:tex></html:li></html:ol></html:p>
          </fr:mainmatter>
        </fr:tree>
        <fr:tree show-metadata="true" expanded="false" toc="false" numbered="false">
          <fr:frontmatter>
            <fr:authors>
              <fr:author>
                <fr:link href="/alex-nelson/" title="Alex Nelson" uri="http://localhost:8000/alex-nelson/" display-uri="alex-nelson" type="local">Alex Nelson</fr:link>
              </fr:author>
            </fr:authors>
            <fr:date>
              <fr:year>2025</fr:year>
              <fr:month>12</fr:month>
